What file formats are supported for export?
We support all major architectural formats including DWG, DXF, SKP, 3DS, OBJ, FBX, IFC, and PDF. You can also export high-resolution renders and 3D models for presentations.
Yes, our AI architecture system is designed for both residential and commercial projects of any scale. It includes advanced features for complex building types and regulatory compliance.

Our AI is trained on engineering principles and building codes. All structural calculations are verified against industry standards, though we recommend final review by a licensed structural engineer.
